    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly stunning condition\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-tucked and spotless. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it\u2019s just pure, pristine perfection. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to a home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come see your dream car!",
      "price": 43500.0,
