    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is a peerless example of the E46 M3, powered by the S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, both recently overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis maintains total structural integrity, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded Powerflex bushings to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 coilover dampers, providing exceptional high-speed stability and cornering flat-ness. Proactive maintenance is documented, including rod bearing replacement and a recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustment. This is a mechanically flawless, investment-grade specimen for the BMW purist.",
      "price": 43500.0,
