    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom state, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior finish is breathtaking, retaining its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied annually; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, with the original leather scent still present and zero signs of wear on the seat bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, documented service history from the authorized dealership, including a recent major fluid service and a fresh set of premium tires. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. The undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork, reflecting a life spent on dry roads and under careful watch. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that has been treated with obsessive care and zero compromises.",
